The paper discusses a framework for autonomous driving that integrates multiple sensors and uses software to process the sensory data. This falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions learning and reasoning, which suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the interaction between the vehicle and its environment, which suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
